OL,3,GNEWSCGood Morning Britain broadcasts
OL,4,Cfrom ITN for first time
OL,5,
OL,6,FToday marks the start of a number of
OL,7,Fschedule and on-screen changes at ITV
OL,8,F1, as part of cost-cutting measures.
OL,10,FThe first changes went live at 6am,
OL,11,Fwith Good Morning Britain broadcasting
OL,12,Ffrom ITN's building for the first time.
OL,14,FGMB previously occupied Studio TC3 at
OL,15,FTelevision Centre in west London.
OL,17,FStudio 1 at ITN is noticeably smaller
OL,18,Fthan the programme's previous home at
OL,19,FTVC.
OL,23,EPub: 05-Jan-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
