OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F155A1773169065
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWSCGood Morning Britain broadcasts
OL,4,Cfrom ITN for first time
OL,5,
OL,6,FDuring its time at TVC (and before
OL,7,Fthat, at The London Studios), the
OL,8,Fprogramme had its own production team.
OL,9,FThis has now been cut and merged with
OL,10,Fthe ITV News operation.
OL,12,FThe new set is a variation on that used
OL,13,Fat TVC, though the main desk is much
OL,14,Fsmaller and there's a new soft
OL,15,Fpresentation area.
OL,17,FThe programme's graphic design is
OL,18,Funchanged.
OL,20,FOther than when wide shots of the
OL,21,Fstudio are shown, the vast majority of
OL,22,Fviewers will notice little difference.
OL,23,EPub: 05-Jan-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,156,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15503
SC,0003
