PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F155A1773169065
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWSCGood Morning Britain broadcasts
OL,4,Cfrom ITN for first time
OL,5,
OL,6,FApart from the modified/smaller set,
OL,7,Fone other on air change is that the
OL,8,Fmain news presenter ` this morning that
OL,9,Fwas Kate Garraway ` also now presents
OL,10,Fthe Good Morning London bulletins.
OL,12,FGood Morning Britain is also on air for
OL,13,Flonger from today ` until 9.30am.
OL,15,FLorraine now starts at 9.30am and is
OL,16,Freduced to 30 minutes. This Morning
OL,17,Fstarts at 10am, with Loose Women
OL,18,Ffollowing at 12.30pm.
OL,23,EPub: 05-Jan-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
