OL,3,GNEWSCGood Morning Britain broadcasts
OL,4,Cfrom ITN for first time
OL,5,
OL,6,FLorraine, This Morning and Loose Women
OL,7,Fhave also departed Television Centre
OL,8,Fand will be broadcast from a shared
OL,9,Fstudio from today ` The H Club studio
OL,10,Fin Covent Garden.
OL,12,FA new schedule for the soaps `
OL,13,FEmmerdale and Coronation Street ` will
OL,14,Fbe marked tonight by a special
OL,15,Fcrossover episode called Corriedale.
OL,17,FThen from tomorrow, a new soap schedule
OL,18,Fformally kicks in: 8pm ` 8.30pm
OL,19,FEmmerdale and 8.30pm ` 9pm Coronation
OL,20,FStreet ` Monday to Friday.
OL,23,EPub: 05-Jan-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
