OL,3,GNEWSCGood Morning Britain broadcasts
OL,4,Cfrom ITN for first time
OL,5,
OL,6,FThis amounts to a cut of one hour of
OL,7,Fthe soaps per week: from six hours to
OL,8,Ffive.
